        public abstract it.unimi.dsi.fastutil.longs.LongOpenHashSet getPoses()

      • contains

        public boolean contains(int n,
               int n2,
               int n3)
        Checks if this BuildHelper contains a location. Effectively calls getPoses().contains(ElementCollections.getIndex(n - placedPos.a, n2 - placedPos.b, n3 - placedPos.c.
        Parameters:
        n - the x coordinate of the location
        n2 - the y coordinate of the location
        n3 - the z coordinate of the location
        Returns:
        True, if the area specified by this buildhelper contains the location in question, false if not.
